Pritalle Nerbaijan,

      Sedai of the Yellow Ajah from Saldaea.  She has green eyes, and an
      unusually small nose for a Saldaean.  She is friends with
      Atuan, which makes those who know about Atuan
      suspicious that Pritalle may also be Black.
